<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Verify Your OTP</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>OTP Verification</h2>
    <p>Hello <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>
    <p>Use the following OTP to verify your account:</p>

    <div class="otp-box"><%= OTP %></div>

    <p>This OTP will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, please ignore this message.</p>

    <div class="footer">
